{"tid":2162040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(蘋果認證) 曹永廉：黃翠如唔係黃屍，直頭係自己友","createTime":"2020-08-18T02:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T04:35:12.000Z","uid":129134,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"506217a7859a35aa49fce41f9918c34b9f983e07","tid":2162040,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"森美套新劇《過街英雄》是非不絕，先有「杯葛界教主」梁振英加持，為咗澄清一段唔係自己打嘅「杯葛文」，而將段文轉載去自己嘅個人平台，不過一眾「信徒」就睇啲唔睇啲，只係睇到「杯葛」部份，於是群起話要杯葛TVB。雖然事後教主有再三澄清，不過已經成功幫森美套新劇造勢，黃藍陣營都等套劇播出。<br />\n<br />\n今日就係呢套劇首播，唔少藍血人都話要罷睇呢套劇，不過「藍血界KOL」曹永廉（Forever Cheap）就睇唔過眼，事關呢套劇係佢死黨蕭正楠個老婆黃翠如有份主演，為咗幫阿嫂力挽收視，<strong>曹永廉就喺FB群組「Save HK」出口術，用自己賬號留言「黃翠如不是黃屍」力證黃翠如不黃，還附上三個雙手合十的emoji。</strong>有網民見到曹永廉個留言，立即回覆問係咪確定翠如藍血人嘅身份？<strong>曹永廉就叫大家信佢，仲留言讚「直頭係自己友」。</strong>見到有藍血界KOL信心認證，有網民即時話：「你係老蕭小三，我信你」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200818/K4ERTZRBQFFEHKPQ2HDMJXE2LU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200818%2FK4ERTZRBQFFEHKPQ2HDMJXE2LU%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkFwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=ecbbddd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200818%2FK4ERTZRBQFFEHKPQ2HDMJXE2LU%2F&h=90c61938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200818/K4ERTZRBQFFEHKPQ2HDMJXE2LU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃翠如扮左咁耐黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340bbe1600161632df0863ce4092fa648bff1a71","tid":2162040,"uid":10905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接d話689係黃咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c2b636bf4cb0ba466ec58566738c4f76389a03","tid":2162040,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"506217a7859a35aa49fce41f9918c34b9f983e07","tid":2162040,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score